{"tid":1765873,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"始創中心一帶應緊急劃成無人區","createTime":"2019-12-02T07:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T16:06:33.000Z","uid":327504,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b544cabbf9a96ee1bf05559c21e6e8305197ce2","tid":1765873,"uid":327504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"有D地方冇咩事嘅去唔去都諗過先, 好似旺角, 始創中心咁<br />\n<br />\nPOPO  本身TG放題, 仲有唔知係咪POPO扮嘅黑衣人燒野有二噁英, 其實呢D位於中心位置, 又唔通風, 粒子又難散嘅地方, 除左對地球叔叔健康有影響, 同時對人有冇呢?<br />\n<br />\n始創中心半徑200米 範圍既建築物同佢哋嘅抽風系統，冷氣糟 外牆呢D位 都極大機會被 大量二噁英同埋山埃嘅微粒依附<br />\n<br />\n至於有冇得解決呀? 成份都唔知, 點解決? 有幾毒, 我相信大家都知.<br />\n<br />\n保守D諗, 如果係附近, 或商場內嘅食材物品因而受污染, 咁就真係要諗下風險<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMybnC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMybnC2.jpg&h=7e3f9715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nuQpHC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnuQpHC3.jpg&h=8defc97e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2320589200832398fc9a7919fdb199645e339cd5","tid":1765873,"uid":240344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔去始創垃圾商場<br />\n又冇人行又冇野行<br />\n仲要之前好多post出過都話佢係藍<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6502883da9f8a977c8aedd6fc62d2ced23a5f5d","tid":1765873,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"[推爆佢] 前線死黑警12月13號觀塘擺酒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1765875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1765875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6734b6b2b65039cab6e8a8ab8c0aa33b6054da1a","tid":1765873,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08d27cd762d42ebb8184050369fa9f939f62fc60","tid":1765873,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T07:5